            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1705422664793-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>baked</strong> <strong>chicken breast & almond curry </strong>with the <strong>baked rice </strong>and<strong> warmed naan[s] </strong>to the side</p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
